templates.prompt_template:
Generate the SAME character from the reference image with the following changes:
- Expression: {expression}
- Pose: {pose}
- Background: {background}

MAINTAIN EXACTLY from reference:
- Face shape and all facial features
- Hair style, length, and color
- Clothing design and colors
- Art style, line weight, and shading technique
- Color palette

Korean webtoon close-up panel:
- Character: {character_name}
- Expression: {expression}
- Emotion conveyed: {emotion}
- Framing: Face close-up, slight {angle} angle
- Lighting: {lighting}
- Background: {background}
- Style: Korean webtoon, wuxia genre, clean detailed linework
- Mood: {mood}
- Quality: High detail, no text

EMPHASIS: Eyes and facial expression should convey {emotion}

Korean webtoon action close-up:
- Character: {character_name}
- Expression: {expression}, battle-ready
- Action: {action_description}
- Framing: Dynamic close-up, {angle} angle
- Lighting: High contrast, dramatic shadows
- Background: {background}, motion effects
- Style: Korean webtoon, wuxia action, bold linework
- Effects: {effects}
- Quality: High detail, dynamic composition, no text

